<p><strong>作品名称：</strong>水滴</p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/josephjoestar" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6159447); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6159447&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600569433" alt="JosephJoestar" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6159447)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/josephjoestar" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6159447); return false;">JosephJoestar</a></span></p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
